com.yworks.yfiles.view.input

Class KeyboardInputModeBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.view.input.KeyboardInputModeBinding
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    KeyboardInputModeCommandBinding, KeyboardInputModeKeyBinding, KeyboardInputModeRecognizerBinding

    public abstract class KeyboardInputModeBinding
extends Object
    A token returned by KeyboardInputMode's factory methods that can be used to remove() the binding again.

    Instances of this class can only be obtained from KeyboardInputMode.addCommandBinding(ICommand, KeyboardInputMode.ExecuteCommandHandler, KeyboardInputMode.CanExecuteCommandHandler), KeyboardInputMode.addKeyBinding(javafx.scene.input.KeyCode, com.yworks.yfiles.view.ModifierKeys, ICommand, java.lang.Object), and KeyboardInputMode.addRecognizerBinding(IEventRecognizer, ICommand, java.lang.Object). Removing the instances is done via the instance method remove() of this type.
